282
00:22:15.870 --> 00:22:16.838
Like ghosts.

283
00:22:16.938 --> 00:22:17.939
That's comforting.

284
00:22:18.039 --> 00:22:19.874
Gotta do one more thing.

285
00:22:19.974 --> 00:22:22.442
