- Thanks.

373
00:27:21.976 --> 00:27:24.613
- <i>Yislamo.</i>
<i>habibi. Shukran.</i>
- Ah.

374
00:27:39.727 --> 00:27:42.564
I didn't realize
how bad an idea this was
until right now.

375
00:27:42.663 --> 00:27:44.899
Smugglers make
my balls itch.

376
00:27:47.434 --> 00:27:49.170
How's your Arabic?

377
00:28:12.627 --> 00:28:14.762
